'''Xawaalad''' {{en|money transmitter, ama money transfer service}} waa meherad ka shaqaysa diritaanka iyo bixinta [[lacag]]ta; taasi oo u adeegta bulshoweynaha caalamka.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ilga.gov/legislation/ilcs/ilcs3.asp?ActID=1201&ChapterID=20 |title=Illinois Compiled Statutes -FINANCIAL REGULATION Transmitters of Money Act|date=January 1, 1995}}</ref>  
Xawilaada lacagta waa [[ganacsi]] weyn oo ka jira dhamaan wadanada caalamka. Wadanka [[Soomaaliya]] waxaa caanka aha xawilaadaha u adeega bulshada kuwaasi oo ukala safriya lacagta meel ilaa meel kale.<ref>{{cite web| url=http://www.fincen.gov/financial_institutions/msb/amimsb.html |title=FinCEN - Am I an MSB |accessdate=June 3, 2013}}</ref> 

Dunida casriga ah maanta, xawaaladuhu waxay isticmaalaan barta [[internet]]ka si adeegooda u fududeeyaan.<ref>{{cite web| url=http://www.law.cornell.edu/uscode/text/18/1960 |title=18 UCS ยง 1960 |accessdate=May 20, 2014}}</ref>

